Analyse the robust regression results by providing a table with descriptives

analyse_meta.Rd

Analyse the robust regression results by providing a table with descriptives

analyse_meta(coeff, t_values)

Arguments

coeff

A dataframe of coefficients
t_values

A dataframe of t-values

Value

A dataframe with the descriptives

Examples

result <- rrs(mpg ~., data = mtcars, k = 4)
coeff <- result[1]
t_values <- result[2]
analyse_meta(coeff, t_values)
